preference.name: DM_IsBatchPrintingEnabled
preference.preference_description: Specifies if Batch Printing is enabled. Valid Values: *true: Batch Printing is enabled. Use this value only when Teamcenter Dispatcher Module Batch Print translator is installed and the Printer Configuration is configured. *false: this is the default value.
